title: Munch Madness: Subway vs 7-Eleven with Lauren Lapkus
itunes:title: Munch Madness: Subway vs 7-Eleven with Lauren Lapkus
description:
Lauren Lapkus (The Wrong Missy, Between Two Ferns: The Movie) joins the 'boys to discuss Nick’s broken toilet before tackling the Desperation Region of Munch Madness 2022: The Tournament of Chompions: Hero's Journey: Sub-Optimal. Plus, another edition of Jingle All The Whey.
